<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Mang Crinkle Admin</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #292524;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
    }
    .email-wrapper {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
    }
    
    /* Admin Container - matching admin design system */
    .admin-container {
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 3px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 1px 2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      border: 1px solid #fed7aa;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .admin-container-header {
      padding: 20px 24px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #fed7aa;
      background-color: #fff7ed;
    }
    
    .admin-container-title {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #9a3412;
      margin: 0 0 4px 0;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }
    
    .admin-container-subtitle {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #ea580c;
      margin: 0;
      font-weight: 400;
    }
    
    .admin-container-content {
      padding: 24px;
    }
    
    .brand-logo {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #ea580c;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .content-section {
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    
    .content-section p {
      margin: 0 0 16px 0;
      color: #374151;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    
    .content-section ul {
      margin: 16px 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
      color: #374151;
    }
    
    .content-section li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    
    /* Admin Button - matching admin-btn-primary */
    .admin-btn-primary {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #ea580c;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 14px;
      text-align: center;
      transition: background-color 0.15s ease-in-out;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
    }
    
    .admin-btn-primary:hover {
      background-color: #dc2626;
    }
    
    .btn-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }
    
    /* Security Notice - matching admin warning styles */
    .security-notice {
      background-color: #fef3c7;
      border: 1px solid #f59e0b;
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    
    .security-notice-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #92400e;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    
    .security-notice-text {
      color: #b45309;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin: 0;
    }
    
    .footer {
      margin-top: 32px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    
    .footer-link {
      color: #ea580c;
      text-decoration: none;
      word-break: break-all;
      display: block;
      margin: 8px 0;
    }
    
    .footer-link:hover {
      color: #dc2626;
    }
    
    .signature {
      margin-top: 24px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #374151;
    }
    
    .signature-name {
      color: #ea580c;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="admin-container">
      <div class="admin-container-header">
        <div class="brand-logo">üç™ Mang Crinkle</div>
        <h1 class="admin-container-title">Welcome to the Admin Panel!</h1>
        <p class="admin-container-subtitle">Your administrator account is ready for activation</p>
      </div>

      <div class="admin-container-content">
        <div class="content-section">
          <p>Hello <%= @admin_user.display_name %>,</p>
          
          <p>You've been granted administrator access to the Mang Crinkle admin system. To get started, you'll need to set up your password and activate your account.</p>
          
          <p>Click the button below to create your password:</p>
          
          <div class="btn-container">
            <a href="<%= @activation_url %>" class="admin-btn-primary">Set Up My Password</a>
          </div>
          
          <div class="security-notice">
            <div class="security-notice-title">üîí Security Notice</div>
            <p class="security-notice-text">This activation link is unique to your account and will expire after you set your password. Please don't share this link with anyone.</p>
          </div>
          
          <p><strong>Once activated, you'll have access to:</strong></p>
          <ul>
            <li>Product and package management</li>
            <li>Order processing and tracking</li>
            <li>Customer inquiry management</li>
            <li>Sales reports and analytics</li>
            <li>User administration</li>
          </ul>
          
          <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to reach out.</p>
          
          <div class="signature">
            <p>Welcome to the team!</p>
            <p class="signature-name">The Mang Crinkle Team</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
          <p><strong>Having trouble with the button?</strong> Copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
          <a href="<%= @activation_url %>" class="footer-link"><%= @activation_url %></a>
          
          <p style="margin-top: 20px;">
            This email was sent to <%= @admin_user.email %> because you were added as an administrator to Mang Crinkle.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 